<div
    class="fixed inset-0 z-50 bg-paper flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen w-full lg:pl-64"
    id="fake-404-component"
>
    <div
        class="max-w-4xl border-4 border-ink p-8 md:p-16 bg-white shadow-neo-lg relative overflow-hidden mx-4"
    >
        <!-- Background glitch decoration -->
        <div
            class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 text-[20rem] font-black text-gray-100 select-none z-0"
        >
            404
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10">
            <span
                class="font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-6 block blink-animation"
            >
                /// SYSTEM ERROR: PAGE NOT FOUND ///
            </span>

            <h1
                class="font-sans font-black text-5xl md:text-7xl uppercase leading-none mb-8"
            >
                Wow, qui non c'è <br /><span
                    class="text-accent underline decoration-4">Niente</span
                >.
            </h1>

            <div class="prose prose-lg font-serif text-gray-600 mb-12">
                <p>
                    Hai raggiunto il vuoto digitale. Probabilmente è successo
                    una di queste cose:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                    <li>Ho sbagliato io a scrivere un link (probabile).</li>
                    <li>Hai scritto male l'indirizzo (possibile).</li>
                    <li>
                        Un cane digitale ha mangiato la pagina (non escluderei
                        l'ipotesi).
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
                <a
                    href="/"
                    class="bg-ink text-white font-sans font-black uppercase text-xl px-8 py-4 hover:bg-accent hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] transition-all flex justify-center text-center"
                >
                    Torna alla Base
                </a>
                <a
                    href="/contatti"
                    class="border-4 border-ink text-ink font-sans font-black uppercase text-xl px-8 py-4 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all flex justify-center text-center"
                >
                    Segnala il guasto
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    @keyframes blink {
        0%,
        100% {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        50% {
            opacity: 0;
        }
    }
    .blink-animation {
        animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
    }
</style>
